<p>Note:</p>

<p><span style="font-size:0.9em; line-height:0%">
<script type="math/tex">% <![CDATA[
\begin{align}
{\rm logit}(p) &= \log \left( \frac{p}{1-p} \right) = a \\[10pt]
{\rm logit}^{-1}(a) &= \frac{\exp (a)}{\exp (a) + 1} = \frac{e^a \cdot e^{-a}}{(e^a + 1) \cdot e^{-a}} = \frac{1}{1 + e^{-a}} = p
\end{align} %]]></script>
</span></p>
